item.title: Swinging fail: a romantic video gone wrong on Pari Island
item.description: On a sunny day in Pari Island, Thousand Islands, Indonesia, a couple's attempt to create a romantic video took an unexpected and humorous turn. In a video captured by @kangkopinyantaiiiii on July 5, 2023, a man was seen inviting his lady counterpart to join him on a swing. Their intention was to create a charming and romantic moment for the camera, but as she attempted to sit beside him, the swing unexpectedly toppled, sending them both tumbling to the ground. With laughter and good spirits, the lady remarked, "The intention was to make romantic-style content like that, instead it fell, it failed."
